{"word":"G4929 - συντάσσω - syntássō - soon-tas-so - Appoint","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συντάσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">syntássō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-tas-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Appoint</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கற்பி"},{"paragraph":"1. to put in order with or together, to arrange"},{"paragraph":"2. to (put together), constitute, to prescribe, appoint"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G5021 - τάσσω - tássō - tas'-so/5021\">G5021</a>; to <i>arrange jointly</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>direct:</i> - appoint.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}